0time%20with%20a%20wall%20outlet%20or%20solar%20panels%20to%20store%20energy%20for%20later.%20I%20wanted%20a%20powerful%20unit%20that%20could%20keep%20me%20comfortable%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20a%20space%20heater%20or%20a%20fan%20%E2%80%94%20and%20plugged%20in%20to%20my%20devices%2C%20and%20power%20appliances%20I%20couldn't%20live%20without%2C%20like%20a%20fridge%20or%20a%20coffee%20maker.%20Their%20uses%2C%20however%2C%20can%20go%20far%20beyond%20emergency%20power%20outages%2C%20with%20applications%20well-suited%20for%20wherever%20you%20need%20untethered%20electricity%20like%20temporary%20off-grid%20living%2C%20camping%20or%20entertaining%20in%20your%20own%20backyard.%20I%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109750986cb-20%26h%3Df7d6be7946d0e5f06241511db9fe2521aab086aa5b0352f31fbc685f7b3174a7%26postID%3D67854e0322e74339bb3b86b1%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fanker-solix-f3800-portable-power-station-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAnker-Batteries-Ultra-High-Generator-Emergencies%252Fdp%252FB0C5C9HMQ2%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnker%20Solix%20F3800%20Portable%20Power%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20versatile%20unit%20for%20home%20backup%20and%20RVs%20that%20has%20enough%20outlets%20and%20capacity%20to%20power%20several%20appliances%20at%20once%20(6%2C000%20watts%20to%20be%20precise).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20months%2C%20I'm%20impressed.%20Beyond%20testing%20its%20limits%2C%20a%20buddy%20borrowed%20it%20when%20he%20lost%20electricity%20and%20wanted%20to%20save%20the%20food%20in%20his%20fridge.%20It%20was%20a%20pain%20to%20schlep%20up%20to%20his%20second-floor%20apartment%2C%20but%20the%20power%20station%20saved%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20on%20lost%20groceries.%20Below%2C%20I'll%20go%20into%20more%20detail%20about%20my%20experiences%20with%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%2C%20who%20it's%20best%20for%2C%20and%20your%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2805573-4ed2-4e63-9c4b-0078800c8099%5C%22%3EDesign%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20closeup%20of%20the%20AC%20outlets%20on%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20portable%20power%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6785582e50dfd88e193e19e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20power%20station%20features%20eight%20AC%20outlets%2C%20including%20six%20of%20your%20typical%20wall%20outlet.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20packs%20a%20lot%20of%20power%20into%20a%20relatively%20small%20footprint.%20Its%20boxy%2C%20vertical%20design%20is%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mini%20fridge%2C%20requiring%20less%20than%20two%20square%20feet%20of%20space.%20The%20attractive%2C%20neat%20appearance%20makes%20it%20suitable%20for%20storing%20anywhere%20without%20standing%20out%20as%20an%20eyesore.%20It's%20undoubtedly%20heavy%20at%20132%20pounds%2C%20but%20heavy-duty%20wheels%20and%20a%20telescoping%20handle%20make%20moving%20around%20on%20a%20level%20surface%20a%20breeze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20power%20station%20has%20tons%20of%20output%20options%20to%20maximize%20versatility%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESix%20standard%20grounded%20(three-prong)%20AC%20outlets%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20NEMA%20L14-30R%20AC%20outlet%20(commonly%20used%20for%20dryers)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20NEMA%2014-50%20AC%20outlet%20(commonly%20used%20for%20RVs%20and%20EVs)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20USB-C%20ports%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20USB-A%20ports%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECar%20socket%20outlet%20(like%20the%20car%20cigarette%20lighter%20of%20yesteryear)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20particular%20note%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20an%20additional%20240-volt%20adapter%20to%20use%20heavy%20appliances%2C%20like%20ovens%2C%20EV%20charging%2C%20or%20dryers.%20You%20can%20plug%20them%20directly%20into%20the%20appropriate%20outlets%20on%20the%20unit.%20This%20versatility%20makes%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20an%20effective%20option%20for%20garage%20workshops%2C%20emergency%20home%20backup%2C%20outdoor%20events%2C%20and%20RV%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22144394e4-d431-41e8-bc3d-e46335d78e99%5C%22%3ECapacity%20and%20performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Several%20items%2C%20including%20a%20humidifier%2C%20laptop%2C%20and%20more%2C%20are%20plugged%20into%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20power%20station.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6785592350dfd88e193e1a73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fan%2C%20humidifier%2C%20electric%20kettle%2C%20and%20charging%20laptop%20didn't%20come%20close%20to%20overloading%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%2C%20which%20can%20handle%20up%20to%206%2C000W%20at%20a%20time.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800's%20base%20capacity%20is%20impressive%20at%203%2C840%20watt-hours%20(Wh)%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20you%20could%20run%20a%203%2C840W%20appliance%20for%20an%20hour%20with%20it.%20Fortunately%2C%20most%20appliances%20are%20well%20under%20that%20size%2C%20so%20you%20can%20run%20them%20for%20several%20hours.%20We'll%20get%20into%20examples%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20purchase%20expansion%20batteries%20from%20Anker%20for%20up%20to%2053%2C800Wh%2C%20so%20you%20can%20slowly%20build%20up%20your%20home's%20power%20backup%20over%20time.%20With%20the%20base%20capacity%2C%20you'll%20have%20enough%20power%20to%20run%20essential%20home%20appliances%20for%20several%20hours%20and%20even%20days%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20this%2C%20I%20plugged%20a%20mini%20fridge%2C%20fan%2C%20and%20light%20into%20the%20fully%20charged%20Anker%20and%20timed