lays%20the%20current%20power%20consumption%20rate%2C%20estimated%20remaining%20runtime%2C%20and%20charge%20percentage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22841e76fd-d172-4646-86af-6f54c89abbfa%5C%22%3EExpandability%20and%20long-term%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%203%2C840Wh%20output%2C%20the%20Anker%20F3800%20is%20a%20great%20short-term%20home%20backup%20option.%20It'll%20keep%20your%20refrigerator%20and%20other%20everyday%20appliances%20running%20for%20several%20hours.%20However%2C%20for%20longer-term%20outages%20that%20last%20several%20days%2C%20you'll%20need%20more%20power.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20Anker%20power%20stations%20are%20expandable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20connect%20up%20to%2014%20batteries%20for%20a%20total%20of%2053%2C800Wh%2C%20which%20should%20keep%20your%20home%20running%20for%20two%20weeks.%20For%20%24400%20extra%2C%20Anker%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ankersolix.com%2Fproducts%2Ff3800-home-backup-kit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20backup%20kit%20with%20the%20F3800%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20connects%20it%20directly%20to%20your%20home's%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20go%20months%20without%20a%20power%20outage%2C%20so%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20much%20power%20the%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20lost%20while%20in%20storage.%20After%20being%20left%20unattended%20for%20two%20months%2C%20the%20power%20station%20maintained%20100%25%20of%20its%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242f9c603-e0fc-4d2c-998d-36ff9687571f%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20portable%20power%20stations%20is%20displayed%20next%20to%20a%20solar%20panel%20in%20a%20yard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68308f0dca50259add4ce716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20my%20cloudy%20town%2C%20I%20rarely%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20utilize%20solar%20charging.%20When%20I%20did%2C%20it%20charged%20much%20slower%20than%20plugging%20the%20Solix%20F3800%20into%20a%20wall%20outlet.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anker%20Solix%20F3800%20is%20only%20barely%20portable.%20At%20132%20pounds%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20move%20up%20and%20down%20stairs%20by%20yourself.%20Fortunately%2C%20it%20features%20durable%20handles%20and%20heavy-duty%20wheels%20to%20assist%20with%20moving%20it%20on%20level%20surfaces.%20As%20a%20home%20backup%20option%2C%20you'll%20mainly%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20power%20station%20in%20one%20place.%20I%20encountered%20issues%20carrying%20it%20up%20and%20down%20the%20stairs%20alone.%20I%20recommend%20having%20someone%20help%20you%20when%20bringing%20it%20to%20remote%20locations%20or%20when%20stairs%20are%20involved.%20An%20extra%20handle%20facilitates%20two-person%20carrying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolar%20charging%20may%20not%20be%20practical%20for%20many%20users.%20When%20I%20initially%20tried%20to%20test%20the%20solar%20panels%20(which%20are%20an%20added%20cost%20to%20an%20already%20expensive%20item)%2C%20it%20was%20the%20dead%20of%20winter%2C%20and%20sunny%20days%20were%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%20Even%20when%20sunny%2C%20I%20needed%20significant%20time%20to%20charge%20the%20power%20station.%20In%20an%20emergency%2C%20you%20may%20not%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20several%20hours%20to%20charge%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnker%20advertises%20that%20the%20F3800%20can%20charge%20an%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20so%20I%20used%20it%20to%20charge%20my%20Chevy%20Bolt%20EUV.%20My%20car%20drained%20the%20fully%20charged%20power%20station%20to%20empty%20in%20three%20hours%20and%20only%20added%206%20miles%20to%20the%20range.%20I%20can%20only%20imagine%20this%20being%20useful%20in%20extreme%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208c17b76-f40d-4ca1-852b-4928293369bc%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20alternative%20that%20comes%20to%20mi