%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20was%20asked%20in%20a%20podcast%20interview%20about%20OpenAI's%20nearly%20%246.5%20billion%20deal%20to%20bring%20Jony%20Ive's%20IO%20startup%20in-house.%3Cp%3EAleksandra%20Szmigiel%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsundar-pichai-google-alphabet-ceo-career-life%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20praised%20Jony%20Ive's%20design%20legacy%20in%20an%20interview%20and%20talked%20about%20AI's%20hardware%20impact.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20acquired%20the%20ex-Apple%20design%20boss'%20startup%2C%20IO%2C%20for%20nearly%20%246.5%20billion%20to%20work%20on%20AI%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIve%20and%20Altman's%20announcement%20coincided%20with%20Google's%20I%2FO%20conference%2C%20echoing%20last%20year's%20news%20drop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20the%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsir-jony-ive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EiPhone%20designer%20Jony%20Ive%3C%2Fa%3E's%20nearly%20%246.5%20billion%20deal%20got%20the%20tech%20industry%20talking%20last%20week%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Google's%20CEO%20has%20now%20weighed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20tech%20leaders%2C%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20is%20leading%20his%20company%20through%20a%20mission%20to%20build%20out%20its%20AI%20empire%20with%20both%20software%20and%20hardware%20products.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20hiring%20war%20for%20top%20talent%20has%20heated%20up%20as%20companies%20spend%20big%20to%20execute%20on%20their%20goals.%20OpenAI's%20latest%20move%20was%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20not-so-secret%20weapon%20whom%20Apple%20had%20long%20leaned%20on%20for%20his%20design%20chops%3A%20Ive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20OpenAI's%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-jony-ive-io-startup-apple-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%246.5%20billion%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20acquire%20Ive's%20secretive%20startup%2C%20IO%2C%20and%20collaborate%20on%20hardware%20with%20his%20design%20collective%2C%20LoveFrom%2C%20Pichai%20praised%20the%20former%20Apple%20design%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStepping%20back%2C%20Jony%20Ive%20is%20one%20of%20a%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said%20during%20an%20interview%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fdecoder-podcast-with-nilay-patel%2F673638%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-interview-ai-search-web-future%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDecoder%26quot%3B%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20Ive's%20storied%20track%20record%2C%20which%20includes%20leading%20the%20design%20of%20iconic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-mac-products-great-classic-boring-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EApple%20products%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20iMac%2C%20iPhone%2C%20and%20Apple%20Watch.%20While%20the%20pair%20have%20met%20only%20a%20few%20times%2C%20Pichai%20said%2C%20he%20and%20many%20others%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20have%20long%20been%20admirers%20of%20Ive's%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichai%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20innovation%20ahead%2C%20and%20I%20think%20people%20tend%20to%20underestimate%20this%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20underscore%20his%20point%2C%20Pichai%20reminded%20listeners%20that%20Google%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20search%20engine%20in%20the%20world%2C%20didn't%20exist%20when%20the%20internet%20was%20invented.%20We're%20in%20a%20similar%20moment%20with%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20Google%20CEO%20said%20%E2%80%94%20except%20he%20predicted%20that%20AI%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbigger%20than%20the%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20going%20to%20be%20companies%2C%