0or%20even%20years%20to%20complete.%20It%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20shawl%20from%20scratch%20until%20completion.%20The%20work%20demands%20a%20lot%20of%20patience%2C%20which%20is%20why%20people%20are%20fleeing%20from%20this%20art%20and%20refusing%20to%20learn%20it.%20It%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20patience%20and%20skill%20that%20define%20this%20timeless%20Kashmiri%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreserving%20art%20amid%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20with%20his%20grey%20flowing%20beard%2C%20adds%20that%20handicraft%20demands%20patience%2C%20a%20quality%20often%20lacking%20in%20the%20younger%20generation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20worked%20on%20a%20project%2C%20a%2064-piece%20shawl%2C%20which%20took%20over%20five%20years%20to%20complete%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20apprentices.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20have%20patience%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20reintroduced%20the%20forgotten%20art%20of%20Jamawar%20shawl-making.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20septuagenarian%20claims%20that%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20there%20is%20not%20a%20single%20artisan%20in%20the%20Valley%20who%20can%20create%20Jamawar%20patchwork%20on%20shawls%20as%20he%20does.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20can%20do%20Jamawar%20work%20like%20I%20do.%20Though%20I%20have%20trained%20many%20people%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20my%20brother%2C%20they%20lack%20the%20accuracy%20and%20dedication%20required%20for%20this%20craft.%20I%20would%20be%20over%20the%20moon%20to%20see%20artisans%20stepping%20into%20my%20shoes%2C%20and%20they%20would%20also%20get%20all%20the%20awards%20I%20receive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Khan%2C%20another%20reason%20Jamawar%20work%20has%20struggled%20to%20progress%20is%20the%20declining%20respect%20for%20handicrafts%20in%20Kashmir.%20A%20growing%20craze%20for%20white-collar%20jobs%20has%20led%20many%20to%20look%20down%20on%20traditional%20artisan%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2